231
00:18:56,840 --> 00:18:59,200
Let me borrow your car and then
I promise I'll have it returned.

232
00:18:59,320 --> 00:19:01,560
My Caddy?
Drive your own damn car.

233
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:03,960
Oh, just let him borrow your
precious Cadillac, for God sakes.

234
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:07,440
There's a perfectly good minivan
sitting out there in the driveway. Here.

235
00:19:07,560 --> 00:19:10,000
What the hell's wrong
with him anyway?

236
00:19:37,280 --> 00:19:40,520
- Tony, thank God!
