something wrong with our man Tony here.

240
00:19:51,080 --> 00:19:52,920
Who is this man?

241
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:56,280
Oh, come on. What is going
on with you two this morning?

242
00:19:56,360 --> 00:20:00,560
Is this like a, uh...
a Christmas joke?

243
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:03,760
"Who is this man?" Well, we're on
the co-op board together, Betty.

244
00:20:03,840 --> 00:20:06,040
And we fought side by side
