245
00:20:06,120 --> 00:20:09,280
And every morning we exchange
quasi-sexual witty banter. Ok?

246
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:11,840
Shall I call the cops?
I'm gonna call the cops.

247
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:14,320
No, I'm gonna call the cops!
You're scaring me.

248
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:17,080
- No, no, no, no.
- Thank you for not calling the cops.

249
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:19,720
Now, I'm going upstairs, I'm gonna
get some sleep. Then I'll be fine.

250
00:20:19,800 --> 00:20:22,280
Sleep you shall. Noblesse oblige
isn't dead. Not yet anyway.

251
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:26,400
Let's, um... Let's get you some help. Surely
there's a shelter somewhere in this city.

252
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:28,400
A shelter?

253
00:20:28,520 --> 00:20:32,400
Hey, hey, are you
smacked out of your head?

254
00:20:32,520 --> 00:20:35,720
I'm the richest man in this building!
I've got twice the square footage you have!

255
00:20:35,800 --> 00:20:38,320
- And I'm going upstairs.
- Take a walk, pal.

256
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:41,000
Oh, not cool.
Not cool!

257
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:43,480
You wanna get cute?
Get cute.

258
00:20:43,600 --> 00:20:46,520
I'm gonna go to my office. I'm gonna file
a complaint to the manager of the building.

259
00:20:46,680 --> 00:20:51,200
I'm gonna have you fired, Tony. And, Mrs.
Peterson, you're on notice with the co-op board!

260
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:54,880
So you better just stop whatever
this is that you're doing!

261
00:21:05,360 --> 00:21:07,920
Oh, come on!

262
00:21:15,320 --> 00:21:18,560
Frank, you won't believe what's been
happening to me. Is Adelle here yet?

263
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:20,480
- Hold it right there.
- Where's Mintz?

264
00:21:20,560 --> 00:21:23,560
The building is closed, pal.
You have to come back tomorrow.

265
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:28,040
Frank, why do I feel the need to remind
you that I'm Jack Campbell, President?

266
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:32,760
I don't care who you are. It's Christmas,
and like I told you, the building is closed.

267
00:21:32,840 --> 00:21:34,800
I don't think
you heard me correctly.

268
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:37,400
I'm Jack Campbell.

269
00:21:37,480 --> 00:21:39,600
Jack Campbell!

270
00:21:41,480 --> 00:21:43,320
President!

271
00:21:50,840 --> 00:21:53,120
Have a nice holiday, man.

272
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:14,760
- That's my car!
- Hi, Jack.

273
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:17,440
