to you, okay?

276
00:22:23,120 --> 00:22:25,960
Come on.

277
00:22:26,080 --> 00:22:27,880
Come on.

278
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:37,480
You're probably gonna wanna
buckle up, Jack. This thing moves.

279
00:22:41,360 --> 00:22:45,400
- What's happening to me?
