down the window and do it out there.

282
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:55,680
Try not to get
so worked up, Jack.

283
00:22:55,800 --> 00:22:57,600
After all, you brought
this on yourself.

284
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:59,720
