287
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:10,080
Bag yourself, Jack.

288
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:16,120
Oh, my God! Ah!

289
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:19,760
The way you intervened in that store last
night, you did a good thing there, Jack.

290
00:23:19,840 --> 00:23:23,520
I mean, it was incredibly impressive
all the way across the board...

291
00:23:23,600 --> 00:23:25,200
to the upper echelons
of the organization.

292
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:28,760
Please just tell me what's
happening to me in plain English...

293
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:31,520
without the mumbo-jumbo.

294
00:23:31,600 --> 00:23:35,000
