in your mouth.

454
00:35:17,600 --> 00:35:20,040
Yeah.

455
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:26,880
- Good?
- Fabulous.

456
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:31,440
At the end of this whole thing, she
made me this hand-embroidered sweater.

457
00:35:31,520 --> 00:35:33,440
- It was really lovely.
- How nice.

458
00:35:33,520 --> 00:35:36,840
